  <brief_title>The Effect of Intraabdominal Saline Irrigation in Abdominal Hysterectomies</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Intraabdominal Saline Irrigation on Infectious Morbidities and Gastrointestinal Outcomes in Patients Undergoing Abdominal Hysterectomies for Benign Causes</official_title>
